text: Gustaf Wretman (10 August 1888 - 17 October 1949) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed at the 1906 Intercalated Games and the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1949 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
